<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

<main class="info-page-main">
	<section class="found-archive" aria-labelledby="lost-found-title">
		<header class="archive-heading">
			<p class="notice-kicker">Recovered from the reeds, mud, and one confused heron</p>
			<h1 id="lost-found-title">Lost &amp; Found</h1>
			<p>To claim an object, describe it convincingly to the desk toad. Bribes of flies are frowned upon but effective.</p>
		</header>

		<div class="found-grid">
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">01</span><h2>One left sock</h2><p>Still damp. Smells faintly of adventure.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">02</span><h2>A tiny golden crown</h2><p>Toad-sized. No questions, please.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">03</span><h2>Waterproof diary</h2><p>Features suspicious bite marks and one very dramatic doodle.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">04</span><h2>Cursed spoon</h2><p>Probably cursed. Definitely a spoon.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">05</span><h2>Three identical pebbles</h2><p>They insist they have never met.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">06</span><h2>Somebody’s dignity</h2><p>Folded neatly beside the jumping rock.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">07</span><h2>A moss-covered key</h2><p>Opens something small, secret, or both.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">08</span><h2>One dramatic love letter</h2><p>Addressed simply: “To the frog by the moonlit log.”</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">09</span><h2>“Probably pond water”</h2><p>One stoppered bottle. Contents refuse to comment.</p></article>
			<article class="found-item"><span class="found-number">10</span><h2>A snail’s racing license</h2><p>Expired, somehow, in a hurry.</p></article>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>

